client_candidates.comment:
We interviewed for  Your Growth Solution (summer sale offer)


Invited candidates for the lead generator  position:


Candidates: 


1. Yelyzaveta P https://rh-s.com/app/managers/lead-generator/yelyzaveta-p

2. Khrystyna Y https://rh-s.com/app/managers/lead-generator/khrystyna-y

3. Margaryta D https://rh-s.com/app/managers/lead-generator/margaryta-d

4. Sergei Y https://rh-s.com/app/managers/lead-generator/sergei-y


Comment:   


Sina Landorff, CEO and co-founder of Your Growth Solution, introduced her company and explained the need for a salesperson.

Your Growth Solution is a remote company focused on team building and team events, particularly targeting tech companies to come to Berlin for on-site events.

Company Background:

The company aims to expand its team from three to eight members.

Currently, the team includes a COO from Taiwan, a legal advisor with an Arabic background, and Sina as the CEO.


Project : Sina clarified the need for a salesperson to help with selling team-building events in Berlin.

Questions were asked about the candidate's ability to generate and qualify leads, set up meetings, and manage communications.


Responsibilities: - to search for leads who runs C level positions and set up calls (CSO, CTO, CFO, CMO). Work with Linkedin. 


Candidate Introductions:


Marharyta: Experienced in lead generation, skilled in using LinkedIn Sales Navigator and other tools.

Yelyzaveta Puzii: Background in translation and remote work, experienced with LinkedIn Sales Navigator, and capable of finding and qualifying leads.

Kristina: Extensive experience in lead generation, working with various tools and platforms, and fluent in English, Ukrainian, and some German.


The interview was productive and insightful, with clear communication about the company’s needs and the candidates’ capabilities. Sina appreciated the diverse skills and experiences of the candidates. 


Yelyzaveta was chosen for her lead generation expertise and her polite and caring demeanor. The onboarding process is set to begin promptly, aiming to start generating leads and setting up meetings as soon as possible.


Next Step: send an agreement and start on Wendsday 24/07. 

Employee - Yelyzaveta P https://rh-s.com/app/managers/lead-generator/yelyzaveta-p

.

Next contact day: WhatsApp group on 24/07/24


SM Margo

SA Julia

name: Nicklas Bødtcher-Hansen
note:
Interested in collaboration.
Product: App, where you can upload your photos.  With SubBook clients can collect, print and share favorite memories with just a few steps.Today everything is digital. Photos and memories are often lost in the virtual cloud. With SubBook they can get all of our favorite pictures printed and perpetuated in a classy and personal photo book. It’s never been easier, and everyone can join in. All need to do is download the SubBook app in the App Store or Google Play.
The company makes it user-friendly, so it is simple to use. Boxes, books are eco-friendly and that all you get in front of your door.

Country- Location: Denmark 

Immediate Requirement: The mission of collaboration is to promote products in our social media, website. To find out all information with CEO of RH about that offer. If it is possible to set up another call and discuss it. Keep in touch by email.
